branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series CVM5 is a double acting, single rod, valve mounted cylinder. Operation style can be changed to normally retracted or normally extended. CVM5 has eight mounting options available and bore sizes range from 20mm to 40mm. Built-in One-touch fittings are also available. A cylinder with the auto switch installed can be manufactured.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;UL&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Valve mounted, double acting single rod cylinder&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Bore sizes (mm): 20, 25, 32, 40&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Available with one-touch fittings&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;8 mounting styles&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Auto switch capable&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;

